<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trang chủ</title>
    <%- include('_share/style'); %>
    <script src=
            "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
            integrity=
            "sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
            crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src=
            "https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity=
            "sha384-oesi62hOLfzrys4LxRF63OJCXdXDipiYWBnvTl9Y9/TRlw5xlKIEHpNyvvDShgf/"
            crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <%- include('_share/header'); %>
    <main class="container-fluid">
        <h4 class="text-center" style="margin-top: 24px;">
            Chào mừng đến trang quản trị của FindJob!
        </h4>
        <h6 class="text-center">
            Tại đây bạn có thể tạo tin tức, xem danh sách, xem chi tiết,
            xóa người dùng; xem danh sách, phê duyệt/hủy phê duyệt
            hoặc xóa các tin tuyển dụng.</h6>

        <div class="container mt-3" style="text-align: center;">
            <div id="slide-show"
                 class="carousel slide"
                 data-ride="carousel">
                <!-- Indicators -->
                <ul class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#GFG"
                        data-slide-to="0"
                        class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#GFG"
                        data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#GFG"
                        data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ul>

                <!-- The slideshow -->
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src=
                             "/images/ic_news.webp"
                             alt="GFG" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src=
                             "/images/ic_users.webp"
                             alt="GFG" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src=
                             "/images/ic_job.webp"
                             alt="GFG" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <a class="carousel-control-prev"
                   href="#GFG"
                   data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon">
                  </span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next"
                   href="#GFG"
                   data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon">
                  </span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('_share/footer'); %>
</div>
</body>
</html>

